{"id":657126,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":7,"day":26}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"社会大学","column":"","genre":"","count":"113","ytitle":"","mtitle":"‘报销’","ftitle":"","authors":["陆路"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在电车站上，听到的一段对话:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——请别忘了，给我弄几张电影票的票根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——派什么用场?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——向工会报销。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——那你每月至少看八部电影的票根呢?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——都是协作单位赠券、招待券。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——哈，真有你的，不出钞票看电影还能报销。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(陆璐)"}]}